Cosmic Gate - Crushed (2013) 

                   House, Progressive, Trance | Black Hole Recordings

              320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2013-07-15 | 00:23:27 | 54 Mb
 



Highly anticipated by the dedicated followers of Nic and Bossi's productions as one of the exclusive tracks on the legendary Trance Nation series mixed by Cosmic Gate, "Crushed" now makes its way to the dance floors in the Mark Sixma remix. Mark Sixma's approach of the original version reaches the levels of plate-tectonics , only counterbalanced with Cosmic Gate's original synth breaks bringing back the track to the realms of trance. Stacking up his seismic beats on top of grinding electro stabs and thundering sweeps, Sixma also gives the sub-bass fanatics something to marvel over.
